                "invention-title": [
                    "Blast furnace smelting method for injecting vanadium titano-magnetite and lignite",
                    "钒钛磁铁矿配加褐煤喷吹的高炉冶炼方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to a blast furnace smelting method for injecting vanadium titano-magnetite and lignite, and belongs to the technical field of blast furnace smelting. The method comprises the following steps that A, ore and coke are fed into a blast furnace, and meanwhile mixed pulverized coal is injected; b, defining the charging conditions of the crude fuel; c, smelting; and D, slag and iron are discharged. According to the method, under the condition that the low-silicon high-alkalinity vanadium-titanium sintered ore, the low-silicon vanadium-titanium pellets or the high-silicon acidic oxidizing pellets and the coke with the high ash content and sulfur content are adopted as furnace feeding raw materials, the high-hydrogen high-volatility low-ash-content low-price lignite is matched for mixed injection, the lignite resource which is rich in resource and low in price is fully utilized, and the energy consumption is reduced; the problems that the vanadium titano-magnetite strengthened smelting utilization coefficient is low, the coal injection ratio is low, the injection pulverized coal source is single, the requirement for the fixed carbon content is high, and anthracite or lean coal resource dependence is high are solved, the utilization coefficient, the coal injection ratio and the air temperature are increased, the desulfurization efficiency and the smelting technical economic index are improved, and the smelting cost and the air consumption per ton of iron are reduced."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及一种钒钛磁铁矿配加褐煤喷吹的高炉冶炼方法，属于高炉冶炼技术领域。其包括如下步骤：A、将矿石、焦炭送入高炉中，同时喷吹混合煤粉；B、对原燃料入炉条件进行界定；C、冶炼；D、出渣、出铁。本发明在采用低硅高碱度钒钛烧结矿、低硅钒钛球团矿或高硅酸性氧化性球团矿，以及灰分、硫分较高焦炭作为入炉原料的情况下，配合高氢高挥发性低灰分低价格褐煤进行混合喷吹，充分利用资源丰富、价格低廉的褐煤资源，解决钒钛磁铁矿强化冶炼利用系数较低、喷煤比低，以及喷吹煤粉来源单一、固定碳含量要求高、无烟煤或瘦煤资源依赖性较强等问题，提高利用系数、喷煤比、风温，改善脱硫效率和冶炼技术经济指标、降低冶炼成本及吨铁风耗。"
                }
